{"content":"1\t\n 2\t<div align=\"center\">\n 3\t\n 4\t![SecExample](https://socialify.git.ci/tangxiaofeng7/SecExample/image?description=1&descriptionEditable=Vulnerability%20environment%20for%20Java&font=Raleway&forks=1&issues=1&pattern=Overlapping%20Hexagons&stargazers=1&theme=Dark)\n 5\tJAVA 漏洞靶场\n 6\t<br>\n 7\thttps://github.com/tangxiaofeng7/SecExample\n 8\t<br>\n 9\t</div>\n10\t\n11\t### 截图\n12\t\n13\t![index.png](images/index.png)\n14\t\n15\t\n16\t### 介绍\n17\t| Name               | Star |\n18\t| ---------------------- | ---- |\n19\t| [注入漏洞-SQL注入]         | 🌟🌟🌟  |\n20\t| [注入漏洞-命令注入]             | 🌟    |\n21\t| [注入漏洞-spel表达式注入]             | 🌟🌟🌟    |\n22\t| [XSS漏洞]            | 🌟  |\n23\t| [CSRF漏洞]             | 🌟🌟    |\n24\t| [SSRF漏洞]             | 🌟🌟  |\n25\t| [CORS漏洞] | 🌟🌟🌟🌟 |\n26\t| [反序列化漏洞-Fastjson反序列化] | 🌟🌟🌟🌟 |\n27\t| [验证码相关漏洞] | 🌟🌟 |\n28\t\n29\t\n30\t### 安装\n31\t\n32\t```\n33\tgit clone https://github.com/tangxiaofeng7/SecExample.git\n34\tcd SecExample\n35\tdocker-compose up -d\n36\t```\n37\t\n38\t访问: http://localhost:8080\n39\t\n40\t[![asciicast](https://asciinema.org/a/gcuay3zNoRUZ85BTPgjpGukuC.svg)](https://asciinema.org/a/gcuay3zNoRUZ85BTPgjpGukuC)\n41","file_path":"/Users/a1024/code/SecExample/README.md","limit":2000,"offset":1}


